icy=\"open\" at: - channels.telegram.groupPolicy Risky tool exposure contexts: - agents.defaults (sandbox=off; runtime=[exec, process]; fs=[read, w…\n    Fix: For open groups, prefer tools.profile=\"messaging\" (or deny group:runtime/group:fs), set tools.fs.workspaceOnly=true, and use agents.defaults.sandbox.mode=\"all\" for exposed agents.\n  CRITICAL Config file is world-readable\n    /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json mode=644; config can contain tokens and private settings.\n    Fix: chmod 600 /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n  WARN Reverse proxy headers are not trusted\n    gateway.bind is loopback and gateway.trustedProxies is empty. If you expose the Control UI through a reverse proxy, configure trusted proxies so local-client c…\n    Fix: Set gateway.trustedProxies to your proxy IPs or keep the Control UI local-only.\n… +3 more\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n┌─────────────┬─────────┬────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Channel     │ Enabled │ State  │ Detail                                                                              │\n├─────────────┼─────────┼────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Stream Chat │ ON      │ OK     │ configured                                                                          │\n└─────────────┴─────────┴────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌────────────────────────┬────────┬──────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Key                    │ Kind   │ Age      │ Model                                 │ Tokens                          │\n├────────────────────────┼────────┼──────────┼───────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────┤\n│ agent:main:main        │ direct │ just now │ bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-