{"type":"message","id":"1395a9a7","parentId":"b75c5547","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:27:55.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Oh okay I see now. That's not Telegram. That's the model.\n\nThe model `kilocode/bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free` is flagging all responses as content filter now. That's why it's stuck in an infinite compact loop. That has **nothing** to do with Telegram. Telegram is working perfectly fine, the messages are getting through. The model is broken.\n\nI will switch us back to the working model right now.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_wcbk7no4nsjuh5j3n64qiut4","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","raw":"{\"agents.defaults.model.primary\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/frontier\"}","note":"Switched default model away from the broken dola-seed one that's hitting content filters."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":36872,"output":200,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775230063723,"responseId":"021775230067267681426abb3fc8758bc9af65311c7ae316d629f"}}
