{"type":"message","id":"c0b699c3","parentId":"ad1c31fa","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:28:05.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]\nOh perfect. Okay so **Telegram is 100% working**. That is confirmed. All your messages are arriving correctly.\n\nThe problem now is **the dola-seed model is completely broken** - it is rejecting every single response with content_filter. That's why it keeps looping the compact message. That's not Telegram, that's the LLM model that just broke.\n\nLet me switch the default model right now to the working one, then restart:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dic8y92totkrbzy0c4ib6q2y","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","raw":"{\"agents\": {\"defaults\": {\"model\": {\"primary\": \"kilocode/kilo-auto/frontier\"}}}}","note":"Switched default model away from broken dola-seed."}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":37124,"output":196,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775230075703,"responseId":"0217752300788868823a6d9d4020aa2a4c8e545461b44d546ec9e"}}
